<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <base href="/" />
    <link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="css/home-style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <script
        src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyBpxLRasLf5ZB87RMgeTxOfpd50bfzYrtE&libraries=places"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9d6133daeb.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.js"></script>
    <title>SOS Bulgaria</title>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar navbar-dark navbar-expand-lg" style="background-color: #000000">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-brand nav-logo">
                <img class="rounded" src="./img/logo.jpg" width="auto" height="50px" />
                <div class="nav-contacts">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                        <p>0899 / 773 232</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                        <p>022 / 23 232</p>
                      </div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>
                        <p>sos@bulgaria.bg</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                    <% if(adminPanel===1) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/admin-panel">Управление на сайта</a>
                        </li>
                        <% } %>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Начало</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/manage-booking">Управление на поръчка</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Услуги</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Контакти</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/about">За нас</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/<%= link %>">
                                    <%= text %>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container-fluid py-5 main-section">
        <div
            class=" opacity-background container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center flex-column flex-md-row">
            <div class="p-3 quote-class">
                <div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                        <h2>Номер на запитване:</h2>
                        <h3 id="quoteNumber" class="font-weight-bold" data-quote-number="<%= quoteNumber %>">
                            <%= quoteNumber.substr(1, 5).toUpperCase(); %>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Цена: <b>
                            <%= quotePrice %>
                        </b>лв</h3>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                        <h2>Час на взимане:</h2>
                        <h3>
                            <%= new Date(new Date().getTime() + 30 * 60000).toLocaleString('bg-BG', { year: 'numeric' ,
                                month: 'short' , day: 'numeric' , hour: 'numeric' , minute: 'numeric' }); %>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Здравейте, благодарим Ви, че посетихте нашия уебсайт. Ако търсите услуга за онлайн
                        резервация на нашите автомобили за рекуперация, ние Ви предоставяме
                        възможността да направите това бързо и лесно, както и да се възползвате от нашата промоционална
                        оферта с код SOSONLINE, която Ви дава 10% отстъпка при плащане онлайн или чрез обаждане на
                        телефонния ни номер:</p>
                    <h1 style=" margin-top: -8px; font-weight: 1000;
                    font-style: italic;">089 / 00 05 000</h1>
                </div>
                <button class="btn__pay-type" id="pay-online-btn">Плати Онлайн</button>
                <button class="btn__pay-type" id="call-us-for-quote-btn" value="0895979200"
                    onclick='()=>{window.location.href = "tel:" + "0895979200"}'>Обади
                    се</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('layouts/footer') %>

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
            <script src="js/pay-quote.js"></script>
</body>

</html>